edge, this is the first end-to-end deep learning method for LF\nreconstruction from a real hybrid input. We believe our framework could\npotentially decrease the cost of high-resolution LF data acquisition and\nbenefit LF data storage and transmission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Feb 2021 06:44:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2022 15:44:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-19"}
