istribution of budget over levels provides practical guidance with theoretical\ninsight as in the celebrated Multi-Level Monte Carlo algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 Feb 2021 15:03:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-16"}
